[09:55.99]NORTHUMBERLAND	I knew of this before; but, to speak truth,
[09:58.70]	This present grief had wiped it from my mind.
[10:01.66]	Go in with me; and counsel every man
[10:04.09]	The aptest way for safety and revenge:
[10:06.63]	Get posts and letters, and make friends with speed:
[10:09.87]	Never so few, and never yet more need.
